@model Sampoerna.EMS.Website.Models.GOODSTYPE.GoodsTypeGroupCreateViewModel


@using (Html.BeginForm("Create", "GoodsTypeGroup", null, FormMethod.Post, new { @class = "form-excise", role = "form" }))
{

    <div class="container-wrap title-page">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-12">
                <h3>Update Excisable Goods Type Group</h3>
                <div class="action-button">
                    <input type="submit" id="SubmitType" name="SubmitType" class="btn btn-blue" value="@Sampoerna.EMS.Core.Constans.SubmitType.Save" />
                    <input type="submit" id="SubmitType" name="SubmitType" class="btn btn-grey" value="@Sampoerna.EMS.Core.Constans.SubmitType.Cancel" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="container-wrap">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-12">
                <div class="white-wrapper">
                    <div class="panel-group" id="accordion" role="tablist" aria-multiselectable="true">
                        <div class="panel panel-default">
                            <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="headingOne">
                                <h4 class="panel-title">
                                    <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                                        Update Excisable Goods Type Group
                                        <i class="fa fa-caret-down"></i>
                                    </a>
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                            @*@Html.ValidationSummary(false)*@
                            <div id="collapseOne" class="panel-collapse collapse in" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingOne">
                                <div class="panel-body">
                                    <div class="form-excise" role="form">
                                        <div class="row">
                                            <div class="col-md-12">
                                                <div class="row">
                                                    <label class="col-md-2">Group Name</label>
                                                    <div class="col-md-4">
                                                        @Html.TextBoxFor(model => model.GroupName, new { @class = "form-control" })
                                                        @Html.ValidationMessageFor(model => model.GroupName)
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="col-md-12">
                                                <div class="row">
                                                    <label class="col-md-2">Excise Group Type</label>
                                                    <div class="col-md-4">
                                                        <div class="row">
                                                            @for (int i = 0; i < Model.Details.Count; i++)
                                                            {
                                                                @Html.HiddenFor(x => x.Details[i].GoodTypeId)
                                                                @Html.HiddenFor(x => x.Details[i].GoodTypeName)
                                                              
                                                                
                                                                <div class="col-md-12">
                                                                    @Html.EditorFor(x => x.Details[i].IsChecked)
                                                                    @Html.Label(Model.Details[i].GoodTypeName)
                                                                </div>

                                                            }

                                                            @Html.ValidationMessageFor(model => model.Details)
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

}

@section scripts {
    <script type="text/javascript" language="javascript">
        $(document).ready(function () {
            $('#MenuMasterGoodType').addClass('active');
        });

    </script>
}